These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, r&b, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person drinking cola is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Music-Genre   | house   | r&b | hip-hop | folk        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the mouse is the fisherman##1
6. the owner of the turtle is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Pet   | goat    | turtle   | guinea-pig     | mouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, havana, pall-mall, fonseca
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the russian is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Cigar   | fonseca       | havana    | prince | pall-mall     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, iris, bellflower
1. the freelancer is the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Flower   | begonia | balloon-flower         | bellflower      | iris        |

