.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, police-officer, journalist, social-worker
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the software-developer is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the police-officer##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Job         | software-developer | journalist    | police-officer | social-worker |

