.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, grapes, watermelon, cauliflower
1. the accountant is the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the mechanic##1
7. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the writer is the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Food   | cauliflower   | cucumber     | watermelon | grapes       |

