.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse, weightlifting, tennis
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Sport        | lacrosse    | weightlifting   | tennis  | snowboarding |

