.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, may, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday          | november     | august   | may | april |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

