3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the fan of funk is the person who growsrose##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who growslily is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b       | electronic | punk      |
| Flower   | rose | orchid  | dahlia    | lily    |

