.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, turtle, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, rowing, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | fish | goat | turtle | bird |
| Sport         | cycling | basketball | tennis  | rowing  |
| Transport     | roller  | snowmobile | van     | subway  |

