.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
House: cape-cod, palace, townhouse, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, chef, lawyer, nurse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, taxi, trike
1. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the chef##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
6. the palace house is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the victorian house is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| House       | cape-cod | palace | victorian | townhouse |
| Job         | accountant | chef  | nurse   | lawyer      |
| Transport   | car        | taxi  | trike   | bus         |

